# Wall-hit detection: lateral distance past the half_width (Q16 m) before
# the slab clamp fires. The clamp pushes the car back to the lateral edge
# and zeros its outward velocity component (analogous to stage_15
# wall_collide). Below the threshold, scraping the wall costs nothing.
const WALL_SCRAPE_THRESHOLD:int = 0      # any penetration counts

